.  sp -1
.  IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
An argument from: \fI[_arguments\-information]\fP found in \fIOPTION\fP, with empty value from man page
(\fIValue Not Found: "${func}", for: "${cmd}"\fP).
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.  sp -1
.  IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
An argument from:_[_arguments\-information]_ found in \fIOPTION\fP (\fI$2\fP),
to indicate the caller to stop parsing and exit (except when called directly (\fI$SHLVL=2\fP), which will exit with \fI0\fP).
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.  sp -1
.  IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
\fIman\fP command not installed (\fICommand Not Found: man\fP).
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
